WEBVTT

00:02.647 --> 00:03.980
You're wrong.
No, I'm not.

00:03.982 --> 00:06.382
Yes, you are.
No, I'm not.

00:06.384 --> 00:08.384
Settle this. Those
little animated pictures

00:08.386 --> 00:11.020
on the Internet, are they
called "gifs" or "jifs"?

00:11.022 --> 00:12.622
Well, the G stands
for "graphics."

00:12.624 --> 00:14.524
That's a hard G,
so I'd say "gif."

00:14.526 --> 00:17.460
W... The guy who invented
it says it's "jif."

00:17.462 --> 00:21.130
I'm sorry, do you mean
the <i> guy</i> or the <i> juy?</i>

00:22.000 --> 00:24.234
Well, I'll give you
three guesses

00:24.236 --> 00:26.236
why I'm so irritated.

00:26.238 --> 00:29.973
Something happened different
from the way you wanted it.

00:30.809 --> 00:32.942
I guess news travels fast.

00:34.045 --> 00:35.745
It's true,
a select group of scientists

00:35.747 --> 00:37.413
was invited
to a weekend symposium

00:37.415 --> 00:39.382
at a former home
of Richard Feynman,

00:39.384 --> 00:41.017
and I wasn't included.

00:41.019 --> 00:43.586
Oh, Sheldon, I'm sure it's
not because they don't think

00:43.588 --> 00:45.455
you're an elite scientist.
Yeah,

00:45.457 --> 00:49.025
I bet you anything it's
just 'cause you're a pain in the ass.

00:49.027 --> 00:52.328
You're just saying that
to make me feel better.

00:53.365 --> 00:55.198
Look, you can spend
the rest of the day

00:55.200 --> 00:57.967
being bitter about this.
Agreed.

00:57.969 --> 01:01.037
I was gonna say "or,"
but why bother?

01:01.039 --> 01:04.674
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:04.676 --> 01:08.011
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:08.013 --> 01:09.646
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

01:09.648 --> 01:12.181
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:12.183 --> 01:14.851
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪<i> We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:14.853 --> 01:17.520
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:17.522 --> 01:19.422
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

01:19.424 --> 01:21.391
♪<i> Bang!</i> ♪

01:21.415 --> 01:25.415
<font color=#00FF00>♪ The Big Bang Theory 8x20 ♪</font>
